WEBVTT

00:01.636 --> 00:03.626
<i>Previously on Camelot...</i>

00:03.628 --> 00:05.836
If we recruit an exceptional
warrior would boost our morale.

00:05.904 --> 00:07.705
- Anyone spring to mind?
- Gawain.

00:09.746 --> 00:13.757
Your king requires your service,
and he demands your loyalty.

00:13.824 --> 00:16.294
There was something
between us. At the coronation.

00:16.364 --> 00:18.534
If you don't feel the same way,
then why did you come?

00:18.602 --> 00:22.241
Just once. Just once.

00:22.309 --> 00:26.151
I know my arrival was difficult for you.
But I'm glad

00:26.219 --> 00:28.355
we could get to know each other.
What do you hope for?

00:28.423 --> 00:31.259
What's in there?
Did I hurt you?

00:31.327 --> 00:33.564
May these rings stand
forever

00:33.632 --> 00:37.539
as a symbol of your unity
and fidelity.

00:39.577 --> 00:42.513
This... power
you've learned.

00:42.581 --> 00:44.450
It costs.

00:44.517 --> 00:47.922
- Don't try and frighten me, Merlin.
- The price will be too high.

00:47.989 --> 00:52.063
No, not too high
at all.

00:54.133 --> 00:58.239
♪

